    {"type": "text", "id": "spa_feats",
     "x": 380, "y": 350, "width": 380, "height": 160,
     "text": "• Cytoscape.js  — graph render (zoom/pan/drag)\n• EventSource — SSE client, incremental graph ingest\n• localStorage — settings + project_id (FR-26)\n• ReactRouter — routes: /upload /project/:id\n• FiltersPanel · EntryPointsPanel · DeadCodeReport\n• PNG/SVG/TXT/JSON export (client-side)",
     "originalText": "• Cytoscape.js  — graph render (zoom/pan/drag)\n• EventSource — SSE client, incremental graph ingest\n• localStorage — settings + project_id (FR-26)\n• ReactRouter — routes: /upload /project/:id\n• FiltersPanel · EntryPointsPanel · DeadCodeReport\n• PNG/SVG/TXT/JSON export (client-side)",
     "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
     "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
     "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
     "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
