    {"type": "text", "id": "backend_feats",
     "x": 900, "y": 350, "width": 460, "height": 160,
     "text": "• HTTP Server + SSE streaming endpoints\n• ProjectLoader — safe ZIP extract (zip-slip check)\n• Parser — AST + types via packages.Load\n• GraphBuilder — nodes/edges from use-def + types.Implements\n• ReachabilityAnalyzer — DFS from entry points\n• Exporter — JSON/TXT for reports\n• Embedded SPA (embed.FS)",
     "originalText": "• HTTP Server + SSE streaming endpoints\n• ProjectLoader — safe ZIP extract (zip-slip check)\n• Parser — AST + types via packages.Load\n• GraphBuilder — nodes/edges from use-def + types.Implements\n• ReachabilityAnalyzer — DFS from entry points\n• Exporter — JSON/TXT for reports\n• Embedded SPA (embed.FS)",
     "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
     "strokeColor": "#ffffff", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
     "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
